title: Common share price of Royal Bank of Canada 1995 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Share price in Canadian dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 25.
In general Share price in Canadian dollars has rose over the Year.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2005 and 2006.
The highest Share price in Canadian dollars, of value 102.75 was reached at Year 2019
Minimum Share price in Canadian dollars about 31.13 was reached at Year 1995
